  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reducing Child Labor through education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is centered at child labor, specifically children bonded in brick kiln industry. The proposed idea is the result of the applicants&apos; experience of three decades which shows that when bonded children get education, they become aware of their rights, are able to handle basic accounts (i.e. calculate income, interest, and other information which is critical to reduce bondage). So, IDA will strive in escaping the bonded children from slavery through providing education at their doorsteps.</narrative>
  </description>
